digitama.name: Tanemon (BT1-007)
digitama.bonus: This card is a reference to the Tanemon who runs the Meat Farm in DW1!
digitama.faq: FAQ: Digivolving in the Breeding Area does NOT count for this card's effect!

digitama.name: Sakuttomon (BT4-001)
digitama.faq: [When Attacking] (once per turn) When this Digimon is LV7, get Memory +1

digitama.name: Bukamon (BT4-002)
digitama.faq: [When Attacking] Discard 1 Evolution Source of 1 of your opponent's LV4 or below Digimon from the bottom

digitama.name: Koromon (BT4-003)
digitama.faq: [When Attacking] (once per turn) When you have 3 or less Security, 1 of your opponent's Digimon gets -1000DP for the turn

digitama.name: Budmon (BT4-004)
digitama.faq: [Your turn] While this Digimon has <Digi-burst>, it gets +1000 DP.

digitama.name: Missimon (BT4-005)
digitama.faq: [Your turn] While this Digimon is [D-Brigade] type, it gets +1000 DP.

digitama.name: Xiaomon (BT4-006)
digitama.faq: [Your turn] While you have 10 or more cards in your trash, this digimon gains <Retaliation>.

digitama.name: Koromon (BT5-01)
digitama.faq: Inheritable: [When Attacking] (once per turn) If this Digimon has [Greymon] or [Omegamon] in its name, <Draw 1>

digitama.name: Tsunomon (BT5-02)
digitama.faq: Inheritable: [Your Turn] If this Digimon has [Garurumon] or [Omegamon] in its name, this Digimon gets +1000DP

digitama.name: Pickmon (BT5-03)
digitama.faq: Inheritable: [When Attacking] If you have 3 or more Digimon, 1 of your opponent's Digimon gets -1000DP for the turn

digitama.name: Yokomon (BT5-04)
digitama.faq: Inheritable: [Your Turn] When this card is trashed due to activating this Digimon's <Digi-Burst>, 1 of your Digimon gets +2000 DP for the turn.

digitama.name: Tsumemon (BT5-05)
digitama.faq: Inheritable: [When Attacking](once per turn) If this Digimon has [Unidentified] in its type, trigger <Draw 1>.

digitama.name: Gigimon (BT5-06)
digitama.faq: Inheritable: [Your Turn] (Once per turn) When another of your Digimon is deleted, this Digimon gets +2000 DP for the turn.
